                {"swissGerman": "Taloon", "german": "Talon/Abschnitt", "explanation": "'Taloon' = 'Talon'. A tear-off slip (from French). Common on Swiss school notices."},
                {"swissGerman": "Znüni", "german": "Zwischenmahlzeit am Morgen", "explanation": "'Znüni' = morning snack (literally 'at nine'). Quintessentially Swiss."},
